      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/ghana-s-deal-with-bondholders-gets-official-creditors-approval</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加纳与欧洲债券持有人达成的债务重组协议获得了官方债权人委员会的批准。]]></description>
