    <item>
      <title>选举结果公布后逢低买入者涌现，法国股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/french-stocks-decline-after-surprise-leftist-win-banks-weaken</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国股市上涨，扭转早盘的跌势，因为在左翼政党意外获胜、议会出现分裂且没有明显多数的情况下，投资者将选举结果视为“最不坏”的情况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/french-stocks-decline-after-surprise-leftist-win-banks-weaken</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 07:17:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Grifols 称创始家族和 Brookfield 正在考虑收购要约</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/grifols-family-brookfield-reported-in-talks-to-bid-for-company</link>
      <description><![CDATA[基立福制药公司 (Grifols SA) 表示，在遭到做空者的攻击导致这家制药商市值缩水数十亿美元后，其创始家族和资产管理公司 Brookfield 已提出收购并将其摘牌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/grifols-family-brookfield-reported-in-talks-to-bid-for-company</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 05:59:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国央行通过增加临时回购来加强对利率的控制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/pboc-to-conduct-temporary-repos-depending-on-market-conditions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着政策制定者扩大引导市场的工具范围，中国人民银行加强了对利率的控制，引入了影响短期借贷成本的新机制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/pboc-to-conduct-temporary-repos-depending-on-market-conditions</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 00:18:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国极左翼政党未能赢得多数席位，股市上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/euro-slips-after-french-vote-as-busy-week-begins-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲股市小幅走高，因交易员们消化了法国提前大选的意外结果，左翼集团没有足够的席位组建政府。欧元抹平了失地，法国债券几乎没有变化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/euro-slips-after-french-vote-as-busy-week-begins-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 22:36:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国大选中左翼政党意外获胜 投资者紧张不安</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/markets-may-warm-to-french-result-after-initial-shock-analysts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国股市周一上涨，因为该国议会选举中最糟糕的情况已经避免。但投资者和交易员警告称，由于政治僵局迫在眉睫，未来几周和几个月市场将出现动荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/markets-may-warm-to-french-result-after-initial-shock-analysts</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 21:26:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
